---
import Button from './Button.astro';
---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-white/70 bg-white/60">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr_1fr] lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-gold">Ives Torres Foundation</p>
      <p class="mt-4 font-display text-2xl tracking-tight text-ink">
        Apoyando a familias con recursos, educacion y comunidad con dignidad y calidez.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">
        La fundacion acompana a familias hispanas y a personas con discapacidad con orientacion,
        talleres, eventos y conexiones comunitarias.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <Button href="/contact" variant="secondary">Contact us</Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink">Quick links</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
        <li><a href="/about" class="transition hover:text-navy">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/programs" class="transition hover:text-navy">Programs</a></li>
        <li><a href="/events" class="transition hover:text-navy">Events</a></li>
        <li><a href="/resources" class="transition hover:text-navy">Resources</a></li>
        <li><a href="/donate" class="transition hover:text-navy">Donate</a></li>
        <li><a href="/news" class="transition hover:text-navy">News</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink">Support</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-muted">
        <li>PayPal available for secure online giving</li>
        <li>Zelle available for direct community support</li>
        <li>Spanish-first experience with English support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
